"title": "8225: devotion",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8225",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Wholehearted commitment to God, to another person or to a task. God's people are encouraged to show such commitment.</p>\n<h2>God's people are to be wholehearted in their devotion to him</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:5\">DEU 6:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:1-Deut30:3\">DEU 30:1–30:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:2\">JDG 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:2\">PSA 119:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:13\">JER 29:13</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of devotion to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:1\">PSA 42:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:7-Phil3:8\">PHP 3:7–3:8</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:6-Num14:9\">NUM 14:6–14:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:11-Num32:12\">NUM 32:11–32:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh14:7-Josh14:12\">JOS 14:7–14:12</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:1-2Kgs23:3\">2KI 23:1–23:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:29-2Chr34:32\">2CH 34:29–34:32</a> <em>Josiah and his subjects</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:12-2Chr15:15\">2CH 15:12–15:15</a> <em>the people of Judah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:1-Ps27:4\">PSA 27:1–27:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:7-Ps40:8\">PSA 40:7–40:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:2\">PSA 84:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:57\">PSA 119:57</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:135-Ps119:136\">PSA 119:135–119:136</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:2\">1CO 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:26-1Cor9:27\">1CO 9:26–9:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:8-2Cor1:10\">2CO 1:8–1:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:13-Phil3:14\">PHP 3:13–3:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:24\">COL 1:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:28-Col1:29\">COL 1:28–1:29</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of devotion to other people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:35\">MAT 26:35</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:31\">MRK 14:31</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:68\">JHN 6:68</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:15-Ruth1:17\">RUT 1:15–1:17</a> <em>Ruth to Naomi</em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:4-1Sam19:5\">1SA 19:4–19:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:12-1Sam20:13\">1SA 20:12–20:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:41-1Sam20:42\">1SA 20:41–20:42</a>EPH <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:22-1Sam5:23\">5:22–5:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:28-Eph5:29\">EPH 5:28–5:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:18-Col3:19\">COL 3:18–3:19</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:1-2Cor8:5\">2CO 8:1–8:5</a> <em>the Macedonian churches to Christians in poverty</em></p>\n<h2>Examples of devotion to a specific task</h2>\n<h3>The leaders and people of Israel to building the temple</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:2-1Chr28:3\">1CH 28:2–28:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:6\">1CH 28:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:9-1Chr28:10\">1CH 28:9–28:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:1-1Chr29:6\">1CH 29:1–29:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:17-1Chr29:19\">1CH 29:17–29:19</a></p>\n<h3>Nehemiah and the people of Judah to rebuilding the walls of Jerusalem</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:4-Neh2:6\">NEH 2:4–2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:17-Neh2:18\">NEH 2:17–2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:13-Neh4:18\">NEH 4:13–4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:21-Neh4:23\">NEH 4:21–4:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:15\">NEH 6:15</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ devoted to his mission</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:51\">LUK 9:51</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:23\">MAT 16:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:33\">MRK 8:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:1-Luke4:12\">LUK 4:1–4:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:1-Matt4:10\">MAT 4:1–4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:16-Luke4:21\">LUK 4:16–4:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:42\">LUK 22:42</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:39\">MAT 26:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:35-Mark14:36\">MRK 14:35–14:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:4\">JHN 9:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:30\">JHN 19:30</a></p>\n<h3>The disciples devoted themselves to the ministry of the church</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:42\">ACT 2:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:42\">ACT 5:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:1-Acts6:4\">ACT 6:1–6:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:4\">ACT 8:4</a></p>",
